      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "frame-02-confidence-rect",
      "originalText": "CONFIDENCE\n\nA capability.\n\nTests tied to important\nbehaviors and failure modes.\nFast feedback. Trustworthy\nfixtures. No flakes.",
